RESULTS
A total of 706 individuals with SCI were included in the analysis (Fig. 1).

claim:
Cardiovascular Risk Profile and Cardiometabolic Syndrome at Discharge
Dyslipidemia was observed in 46.7% and impaired fasting glucose was seen in 26.1% of the cohort (Fig. 2).
title: FIGURE 2.
caption: Cardiometabolic risk profile of individuals with SCI on discharge.
